and produce radiation.

00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:22.940
And this is actually what
we have done last time.

00:01:22.940 --> 00:01:26.780
And what we concluded
is that if you

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:29.990
want to produce
electromagnetic waves,

00:01:29.990 --> 00:01:33.800
you have to introduce
acceleration

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:37.320
