you will be able to produce

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:38.890
electromagnetic waves.

00:01:38.890 --> 00:01:43.210
And also, we have derived, based
on geometrical arguments, what

00:01:43.210 --> 00:01:48.040
would be the magnitude
and the direction

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:52.920
