acceleration of this charge

00:02:44.180 --> 00:02:46.760
to somewhere which is
very, very far away.

00:02:46.760 --> 00:02:50.090
Therefore, the
acceleration, a perp,

00:02:50.090 --> 00:02:52.760
is evaluated at
t prime, which is

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:57.770
t minus r/c, the amount
of time for the speed

00:02:57.770 --> 00:03:01.960
of the information traveling
at the speed of light.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:07.550
